-- Brazil's Cocoa Grindings Advance 13% in August Over July, Hartmann Says
-- Stuart Wallace
-- 2010-09-20T07:40:18Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-20/brazil-s-cocoa-grindings-advance-13-in-august-over-july-hartmann-says.html

          
          
             Brazilian cocoa grindings reached
324,924 bags in August, 13 percent more than in July, analyst
Thomas Hartmann said in a report.  
 The figure was 3.6 percent more than the 313,600 bags a
year earlier, the Salvador-based analyst said.  
          
          


  


        